{"tid":2122523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衛生署公布25間用作隔離的酒店名單","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T03:20:09.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5296e7a6f6af84544c99a2a7cc7f93ecc0ed673c","tid":2122523,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"政府公布25間酒店的名單，這些酒店讓14天內曾在9個指定地區停留的抵港人士入住，接受14天隔離檢疫。名單涉及12間港島區酒店，而九龍和新界分別有10間和3間。 <br />\n<br />\n衛生署指，名單所列的酒店，包括由香港酒店業協會，以及香港酒店業主聯會轉介和直接參與的酒店。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348751&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=3507e74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348751</a>"},{"pid":"478c1c0349623f9c648a93c213102834fb207c9a","tid":2122523,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/inbound/hotels.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Finbound%2Fhotels.pdf&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=538b454d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/inbound/hotels.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"a6d12359f193e02d1d8b36830defdd2ae39c7788","tid":2122523,"uid":21470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"你班酒店業仆街，醫護book 房就唔撚得<br />\n共產黨餵飯你食，就大開口，食撚死你呀"},{"pid":"6fca440a0534e7d1b26be9accff83f045db6f3a0","tid":2122523,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc237d410aac4cd0bd7f46e8c7d128072fc2140f","tid":2122523,"uid":68261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"parklane係正鬧市都有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hk